{"tid":2472081,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"《魔瞳》一次換眼，讓我變成魔鬼（原來今年已過四分一...）","createTime":"2021-04-02T05:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T20:19:35.000Z","uid":44674,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"727154c73abe99f1dfebd7753d58c929121c37b3","tid":2472081,"uid":44674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQN5MPX8mU7aaWnmXuQYjW3fCs94qY4aemnVmcMnwK79J?filename=Gz2w3FW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGz2w3FW.jpg&h=afc5a5c9&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">實體書卷一至五現已發售</span></strong></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"></p><p class=\"center\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sRJZ7p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sRJZ7p&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=6777cde1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sRJZ7p</a></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">簡介</p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  太古之初，天上唯一以六天創造大地，安息一天。當時的天使長路斯化，趁機率領天上三份一的天使，反抗天上唯一，可惜最後失敗收場。成王敗寇，這群天使最終被天上唯一以大能制服，折斷翅膀，剝奪「永生」的資格，並貶下凡間，成為魔鬼，以人類的慾望和負情緒為生。 <br />\n<br />\n  『魔瞳』，就是魔鬼眼睛的意思，而每個魔鬼，身上都必定會有一顆或以上的『魔瞳』。在一般情況下，『魔瞳』的外表和普通眼球沒分別，只有當魔鬼發動異能時，『魔瞳』的眼瞳顏色才會被魔氣刺激，變得赤紅。眼瞳的紅色越是鮮艷，表示那魔鬼體內的魔氣越是精淳。 <br />\n<br />\n  主角畢永諾，自幼生性孤癖，在十六歲的某天，他突然被一陌生男子強行塞上『魔瞳』，蛻變成魔。後來，他慢慢了解到，自己的命運天生就連繫著天下群魔，以及世界末日的秘密...... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網購《卷一》至《卷五》<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sRJZ7p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sRJZ7p&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=6777cde1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sRJZ7p</a><br />\n紙言 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shikoto.com/i/sP \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fi%2FsP%20&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=2684760a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.shikoto.com/i/sP </a><br />\nFACEBOOK 專頁 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/bonnaannob\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbonnaannob&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=280122b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/bonnaannob</a><br />\nPenana<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story.php?id=54188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory.php%3Fid%3D54188&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=7aa76e2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story.php?id=54188</a><br />\n<br />\n(歡迎追殺...)"},{"pid":"4cec22966ad9edf6d6c5adaf0f64adcf8a4aa1b6","tid":2472081,"uid":55858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"開新po 冇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f695ddfef651ce41f5a0419526dd906c7bec378","tid":2472081,"uid":192541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b126b5e78870e105ff9f8ee8e2fda21d0e8aa663","tid":2472081,"uid":16607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dbe6593071298319d8567cacface63af2c8621","tid":2472081,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T06:07:36.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c0e2b07655100c040055b24fc0da1c57cc08c012","tid":2472081,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n新po 冇文<br />\n<br />\n仲要推返拋西瓜po<br />\n<br />\nWeak Po Lau Ming<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmetuvbr6N6CLuA7r2A5uX2RPo7H5Vo41FWoGcKSd32scW?filename=uGzfE23.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGzfE23.gif&h=97543a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeiJA4NrnSq2QqyFcmaBKSUgEj9PVZGz9WgL61P1zrqVE?filename=9GMB2zJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.